  "prompt": "Can a Guitar Hero guitar be used in Rock Band?",
  "response": "Yes, in some cases, a Guitar Hero guitar can be used with Rock Band, but compatibility depends on the specific models of the guitar and the gaming systems you are using. Generally, PlayStation and Xbox systems have their own compatibility standards. For example:\n\n- **Guitar Hero for PlayStation 3**: Guitars designed for PS3 may work with Rock Band games on the same system.\n- **Guitar Hero for Xbox 360**: Similar to the PS3 situation, Xbox 360 Guitar Hero controllers may work with Rock Band on the same console.\n\nHowever, this cross-compatibility does not apply universally, and many players report mixed results. It's best to check the specific compatibility of your guitar model with the Rock Band game version you are using. If you are playing on a different console, the chances of compatibility may decrease significantly.",
